messages.text:
So I know a boy who's sleeping just 4 hrs a day for last 2.5 weeks, having 1 or rarely 2 meals a day in the time period, who has lost around 3kg weight in that time, who has been regularly travelling for sponsorships all around the town in scorching heat. 
I laugh soo hard while thinking of him, he had soo much work. He thought he was some bigshot, being the Art Club secratary, there was a fest coming so everything was on his head, and he had many club members to help but that added him extra work of management too 😂
He thought it'll be easy.. 😂😂

He was out of contact with everyone, he goes to room at around 2-3 am and goes down back at around 7-8 am. He's been missing classes for so long and has no idea what's going on. 

And no one cares if he's doing fine, all he gets is more work calls and the opinions from all sides that this could have been done like this, like that 😂😂

He's out of contact with everyone, but rather than thinking of him, everyone just thinks he's avoiding them. And how pathetic, he has to explain himself to everyone like a culprit 😂😂😂

Even his mom was saying even now he won't call, what will be the situation in future 😂😂. And 3 fest days running here and there, still he has to explain everything to everyone, who cares 🤣🤣

Such a lowlife, I can't stop laughing thinking about him 😂😂
